  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd 6 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1 \u0b89\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0ba9 \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b95\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc2\u0bb1 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1 - \u0b95\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb9\u0b9a\u0bc0\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "We cannot guarantee that Sri Lanka will receive any assistance for the next 6 months - Kabir Haseem",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "United People's Shakti has initiated negotiations with various international organizations including the International Monetary Fund.",
        "MP Kabir Hasim said that based on their observations, it is not possible to say with certainty that any assistance will be available for the next 6 months.",
        "He was speaking at a press conference held at the office of the Leader of the Opposition in Colombo on Thursday (30).",
        "This government has completely lost faith in the international community. So it is questionable whether international aid will be available.",
        "Political and economic changes are essential in the country right now. An all-party government should be formed for this.",
        "The reason is that the situation is worse now than during the war. Even the sovereignty of the country is affected.",
        "Everyone must act with commitment without any discrimination to save the country from this crisis.",
        "We are in talks with various international organizations, including the International Monetary Fund.",
        "Based on them, Sri Lanka will not receive any international assistance for the next 6 months. Therefore, it is not acceptable to say that the situation will improve in the next 3 weeks."
      ],
